<p><span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">Sabrimala, justice indu malhotra</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:19px">
<li><span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"><span style="font-size:11.0pt">Courts should not venture to rationalise matters of religion and faith and courts cannot undertake judicial review of the same, she opined.</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"><span style="font-size:11.0pt">rejected =&nbsp; exclusion on physiological basis is a form of untouchability</span></span>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:52px">
<li><span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"><span style="font-size:11.0pt">said it was about the celibate nature of the deity and not about women of a certain age</span></span></li></ul></li></ul>
